{"tid":709733,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"求各路師兄幫忙，想請教澳洲tafe Cert 3 和4在港的認証","createTime":"2018-06-20T08:59:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T06:22:48.000Z","uid":189627,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"886b8e990939f77b4e897bb42f5129239988a858","tid":709733,"uid":189627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T08:59:51.000Z","msg":"請問各位師兄知道 mechanical 的Cert 3 和 4的認受性高嗎? 資歷是等同香港的多少等級<br />\n<br />\n可以有少許機會申請到機械工程的大學或只能申請diploma還是什麼也不能申請☹️<br />\n<br />\n本人只知道在澳洲可以用Cert 4申請大學但括免的科目沒有diploma多，不知道香港是否也一樣，求各路大神幫忙"},{"pid":"ffc7c01c14c8c933c11991ee7e4d9c1c66aad210","tid":709733,"uid":170547,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T12:43:01.000Z","msg":"大陸狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28e3b81a041246a446e476bdb642dc0b3fcb1b71","tid":709733,"uid":19920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T23:39:14.000Z","msg":"無用"},{"pid":"948b8ef2bb1d219d93185f44f83a51011b043bdf","tid":709733,"uid":189627,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"28e3b81a041246a446e476bdb642dc0b3fcb1b71","tid":709733,"uid":19920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T23:39:14.000Z","msg":"無用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T14:42:58.000Z","msg":"姐係完全吾承認家師兄?甘知吾知算係咩資歷啊?"},{"pid":"472881dfcc9e3b8e01999502c5d819b62b129300","tid":709733,"uid":7391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T14:58:58.000Z","msg":"可以試試交齊文件比幾千蚊去學術評審委員？度秤下，睇佢比唔比返個資歷架構你"},{"pid":"96822681737fbdc5377abe4d537ce3f07a12fd7d","tid":709733,"uid":189627,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"472881dfcc9e3b8e01999502c5d819b62b129300","tid":709733,"uid":7391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T14:58:58.000Z","msg":"可以試試交齊文件比幾千蚊去學術評審委員？度秤下，睇佢比唔比返個資歷架構你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T02:46:03.000Z","msg":"吾該你先"},{"pid":"dd3a52bd0ff709f7a55e093775184e25cec3729f","tid":709733,"uid":235224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:12:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0ba1700feb76abc944e8bf02a3f1d82b221d4375","tid":709733,"uid":235224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:12:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"42a2ba7f40f268ab7b2bf9d5f9fb53a4417e1961","tid":709733,"uid":235224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:13:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"79076e0eb8dcf3de92f641957388b71b0d5596a3","tid":709733,"uid":235224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:14:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4e9d5413d32754cd6e148117c86210a5fe769905","tid":709733,"uid":235224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:14:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8ea0599a35bc458e85622c10ea4558dd8e5c9ad8","tid":709733,"uid":235224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:14:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3af9574712de98ca3a4f6e06fad1f2ca5e45259f","tid":709733,"uid":7828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:22:48.000Z","msg":"各位DSE學生報讀任何課程前，請先查詢有關課程是否有HKQF（香港資歷架構）的認可，切勿因為一時大意誤信他人被騙。<br />\n<br />\n資歷名冊官網<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkqr.gov.hk%2FHKQRPRD%2Fweb%2Fhkqr-tc%2Findex.html&d=f1ak%2FKx76gFv0bJ44sDKYAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=cf9232f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n資歷搜尋<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/search/qr-search/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkqr.gov.hk%2FHKQRPRD%2Fweb%2Fhkqr-tc%2Fsearch%2Fqr-search%2F&d=f1ak%2FKx76gFv0bJ44sDKYAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=3c90f473\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/search/qr-search/</a><br />\n<br />\n基本上傳銷或者詐騙的人，他們喜歡先入為主，不停感情勒索，裝作大家感情深厚<br />\n<br />\n帶你去見工：<br />\n「要為屋企人著想，賺多啲錢」<br />\n「讀大學冇用㗎，呢份工先有錢途」<br />\n「有錢途再追逐自己夢想都唔遲」<br />\n「好自私，只顧及讀書，真係好好好自私，錢又媽比，家境又5好，明知讀完得萬幾蚊，照顧5到屋企，你又讀得5勁，點解要讀？」<br />\n「問你要揀買樓定讀大學，又問你憑咩講話冇時間讀書（因為平時有出黎發夢）<br />\n<br />\n帶你去傳銷學校 ：<br />\n「我想你改變自己」<br />\n「唔好輕易放棄，放棄自己將來」<br />\n「ive/副學士/hd 冇用㗎」<br />\n「想識d有上進心嘅男仔」<br />\n「d顧問好嚴格，記得帶齊所有身份證明文件/證書」<br />\n「張證書有poly 認可㗎，你讀其他之後出嚟做嘢冇用點算」<br />\n（poly 你老母，打過去poly 話唔撚係，只係出席活動的證書，唔會有咩學歷證明，食屎啦臭雞)<br />\n<br />\n帶你去美容：<br />\n「我帶你去做facial呀/你陪我去做facial呀」<br />\n「我當你是朋友才給你這優惠」<br />\n<br />\n[轉貼］<br />\n<br />\n透過 HKG 分享一則貼文：[大學生小心職場陷阱] 小心有傳銷公司成員係交友app 扮係你朋友<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164242/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F7164242%2Fpage%2F1&d=f1ak%2FKx76gFv0bJ44sDKYAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=35c2384b\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164242/page/1</a>"}]}